{"tid":1641352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[馬鞍山] 手足小心陷阱，商場公共空間","createTime":"2019-10-09T10:11:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T18:45:47.000Z","uid":137789,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a3a6ba8ff9e73566161ec2705d6191ee04a5edfd","tid":1641352,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:11:33.000Z","msg":"手足小心陷阱<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1045212\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1045212&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNoGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=45671e71\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1045212&h=e8054153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1045212</a><br />\n馬鞍山神秘公共空間&mdash;&mdash;馬鞍山廣場及新港城中心天幕廣場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20161007/55745953\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20161007%2F55745953&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNoGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=e4cd2c11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20161007%2F55745953&h=fbaed356\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20161007/55745953</a><br />\n地政處證新港城出租公共空間違契 促業權人糾正<br />\n恒基屬下的馬鞍山新港城中心疑出租商場內用作通道的公共空間，用作舉辦食品展活動牟取私利。展覽地點位於新港城中心2樓，是新港城及耀安邨一帶居民來往馬鐵站的主要通道。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N4O3rZK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN4O3rZK.jpg&h=8a14d47a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"467665b4711db7c606b18cceb08c80a0970f6416","tid":1641352,"uid":235277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:14:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ebf4ce7846abf42e02573b464e36be7a47bca285","tid":1641352,"uid":266172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:14:23.000